DESCRIPTION:Come join us in the fields to lose track of time\, be outdoors
 \, practice embodied work\, and experience profound community with plants
 \, soil\, and humans! Our students\, volunteers\, and staff consistently 
 say that their most memorable memories at DCF are the conversations they 
 shared over a wheelbarrow of mulch or while tackling weeds in a bed of ca
 rrots together. Absolutely no farming experience is necessary\, and there
  is no Duke affiliation required. We have tasks for most ages and abiliti
 es.
DURATION:PT3H
