DESCRIPTION:Join us to learn about community care practices as situated re
 sponses to gender-based violence and urban precarity in León\, Guanajuato
 \, Mexico through research by Marcia Moreno Benítez (independent research
 er)\, with a response from Verónica Gago (UBA\, UNSAM\, CONICET)\n\n️ Wed
 nesday\, April 8\, 2026\n⏰1:25-2:40 PM (EDT)\nOnline (Zoom - Translated c
 aptioning available)\nRegistration free but required: https://www.eventbr
 ite.com/e/cuidado-comunitario-tickets-1986088985620?aff=oddtdtcreator&kee
 p_tld=true\n\n Presenter / Presenta:\n\nMarcia Moreno Benitez (ITESO)\n\n
 "Cuidados comunitarios como contracara de la violencia de género en conte
 xtos de precariedad urbana: un estudio de caso en la periferia urbana de 
 León\, Guanajuato\, México"\n\n"Community Care as a Counterpart to Gender
 -Based Violence in Contexts of Urban Precarity: A Case Study in the Urban
  Periphery of León\, Guanajuato\, Mexico"\n\nRespondent / Responde:\n\nVe
 rónica Gago (UBA)\n\n Paper(s) (written in Spanish) will be circulated pr
 ior to the event / Manuscrito(s) (escrito en español) se circulará antes 
 del evento\n\nℹ️ Speakers will be presenting in Spanish with translated c
 aptioning avaliable on Zoom. Q&A open in both Spanish/English / Ponentes 
 presentarán en español con subtítulos traducidos disponibles en Zoom. Las
  preguntas y respuestas estarán abiertas en español e inglés.
DURATION:PT1H15M
