DESCRIPTION:The AI landscape is evolving rapidly and the growing number of
  tools\, models\, and use cases can feel overwhelming.   \n\n  \n\nThis s
 eminar will introduce the Duke Health AI Studio and Microsoft Copilot\, c
 larify how each fits into the Duke Health ecosystem. Through practical ex
 amples and real use cases\, you'll learn how these tools support research
 \, administrative efficiency\, data analysis\, and experimentation-while 
 keeping PHI secure. Designed for beginners through advanced users\, this 
 presentation helps you move confidently from curiosity to effective AI us
 e.
DURATION:PT1H
DTSTAMP:20260210T161308Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T120000
LAST-MODIFIED:20260210T161308Z
