CREATED:20260331T201819Z
DESCRIPTION:Duke SEDS is hosting Dr. Steven Platnick\, a leading atmospher
 ic scientist with over three decades of experience at NASA\, to speak. As
  the former EOS Senior Project Scientist and longtime lead for MODIS and 
 VIIRS cloud algorithm development\, his work has been critical to improvi
 ng our understanding of Earth's climate system. In this talk\, Dr. Platni
 ck will share insights from his career in satellite remote sensing and at
 mospheric research\, followed by a Q&A session.
DURATION:PT1H30M
DTSTAMP:20260331T201819Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T170000
LAST-MODIFIED:20260331T201819Z
